movie_name: Vinnie-isms: The Story of the Cop Comedian
short_description: A Deputy Sheriff turned comedian, Vinnie Montez found humor helped him cope with job trauma. He shares stories from law enforcement, family, and Mexican heritage in shows worldwide.
